fields.name: AdditionalEgressEndpoints
fields.description: The list of egress endpoints. This allows for connection from a Hybrid AKS cluster to the specified endpoint.

fields.name: AssociatedResourceIds
fields.description: The list of resource IDs for the other Microsoft.NetworkCloud resources that have attached this network.

fields.name: ClusterId
fields.description: The resource ID of the Network Cloud cluster this cloud services network is associated with.

fields.name: DetailedStatus
fields.description: The more detailed status of the cloud services network.

fields.name: DetailedStatusMessage
fields.description: The descriptive message about the current detailed status.

fields.name: EnableDefaultEgressEndpoints
fields.description: The indicator of whether the platform default endpoints are allowed for the egress traffic.

fields.name: EnabledEgressEndpoints
fields.description: The full list of additional and default egress endpoints that are currently enabled.

fields.name: HybridAksClustersAssociatedIds
fields.description: Field Deprecated. These fields will be empty/omitted. The list of Hybrid AKS cluster resource IDs that are associated with this cloud services network.

fields.name: InterfaceName
fields.description: The name of the interface that will be present in the virtual machine to represent this network.

fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: The provisioning state of the cloud services network.

fields.name: VirtualMachinesAssociatedIds
fields.description: Field Deprecated. These fields will be empty/omitted. The list of virtual machine resource IDs, excluding any Hybrid AKS virtual machines, that are currently using this cloud services network.
